Name: Bartolo laura
Categories: Books & Literature, Education, Fashion/Beauty/Lifestyle, Fitness, Food/Cooking, Gaming, Health & Wellness, Outdoors/Camping/Hiking, Parenting & Family, Pets & Animals, Technology, Travel
Comments:
Hi! My name is Laura, I’m 31 years old, a mom of a 3-year-old little boy, and a passionate UGC Creator based in France.
I create authentic, aesthetic and impactful content that helps brands connect with their audience in a real and engaging way.

My main niches are:
Parenting, Fitness, Health, Beauty (Haircare), and Lifestyle.
As a mom and entrepreneur, I understand what it takes to speak directly to real people with real needs.

I’ve worked with several brands on product testing, reels, stories, and tutorials  always aiming for honest reviews and value-driven content.

If you’re looking for a creator who brings both creativity and sincerity, I’d love to collaborate!
Let’s bring your brand to life through my lens.
Equipment: I use two professional cameras, my smartphone for flexible shooting, a professional Edgee microphone for clear audio, and Neewer lights to ensure great lighting. For editing, I rely on professional video editing software to deliver high-quality, polished content. This setup allows me to create versatile, engaging content that meets brand standards.
Motivation: I'm excited to work with Linkvids because I see it as a dynamic platform that values authentic content and real connections between creators and brands. As a UGC creator, my goal is to deliver content that feels genuine, relatable, and engaging, and Linkvids aligns perfectly with that vision. I’m motivated by the opportunity to collaborate with brands that trust creators to tell real stories. I believe Linkvids offers the right space for that kind of creative partnership, and I'm excited to grow, learn, and connect with a wider network of like-minded professionals.
